article_title: New Nevada Health-Exchange Chief Faces Technology Shift
article_text:
Nevada’s health exchange will look different this time around.

After a bumpy first year, the exchange has uncoupled from its technology provider, Xerox Corp., and...

twitter.description: The new leader of Nevada’s health-insurance exchange faces big challenges, including making it all work after the site parted ways with its former technology provider, Xerox.
